reviewText: CD only worked on a computer and not on any cd player.  returned and reordered and still did not work, returned.  will buy somewhere else.
It was a gift, recipient really enjoyed it.
Nice Christmas album for one's holiday mix.
Very good live.  Most (if not all) hits were present.

Love this CD!  Definitely one of my "new" favorites for the holiday season.  The songs & music & background stories just put you in the mood for Christmas.
I would highly recommend it to anyone.
Nice concert, just ok.
A wonderful album of favorite and original Christmas music.  Harmony provided by the voices plus the atmosphere and mood created for the Christmas season is worth adding to your annual celebration.
Great dvd
great over all
I purchased this as a gift for my cousin. He loved it!
The singing the classics Christmas songs that we all enjoy listing to they also take the time to tell what they did on Christmas and what they do now therefore I give this 5stars.
Like it
St. Nick's Gift
great DVD
Great DVD and looking forward to using it during the Christmas holidays.
Lady Antebellum really went all out on this presentation.  Great job and so happy to be able to get this one.  Thank you for presenting it for purchase.  Love it!  Diane
They are great and any who buy's the DVD will not be disappointed. It is great even my grand children who not CW fans love it.

Definitely brings Christmas into your home with Lady Antebellum wonderful selection of Christmas Songs....
For all ages young & old brings wonderful memories which warms the hearts for the holidays....

My wife, daughter and I were actually at the recorded performance in Nashville when this DVD was made!  We had a great time and it made a wonderful keepsake of the evening with my two girls.  Great job on the production  and the environment for the show was fantastic.  True Lady A fans will love this delightful holiday special.

Very nice concert and Christmas show.
I will watch for years to come .It can be a holiday tradition in my home .
Fabulous!  Best Christmas DVD in a very long time. Beautiful songs and just shows how talented they are. Would definitely recommend.

I purchased this to play in the background during our Christmas party.  I played it on a projector and played it using a receiver and high quality bookshelf speakers.  The results were great.  The sound coming from this DVD is better than what I could get out of a CD.  Very rich and clear.  Plus it has some comments throughout about the group and those were a great plus of Lady Antebellum fans.

Pros:
Great Sounds
Good Picture
Great for social gathering.

Cons:
None
I received the CD quickly but it would not play.  I tried it in 3 different cd players - NOTHING!  Had to return it.  It's a busy time of year so I didn't appreciate the wasted time.
Bought this for Christmas and it is wonderful. If you are a Lady A fan this will be something you definitely will want to get.
Threw it in the bluray player and let it play through a couple times as we celebrated Christmas. Also had Home for Christmas with the Celtic Women, another good one!

Loved the DVD. They sang almost all the songs from their Christmas cd. I have watched several
times this Holiday season.
The performance footage was very good.  I enjoyed the backstage, informal songs also.  The audio quality is excellent.  It has a personal feeling to it.
The CD doesn't even work!!! Put it in the CD player and nothing happens but a swishing noise and no music!! Very disappointed a CD like this would get sent to a customer.

I really enjoyed Lady Antebellum's On This Winters Night Christmas Music DVD. I like their versions of the old Christmas classics. I especially enjoyed Silent Night the way they arranged it. There are many bonus features that where fun to watch also. Very well done.
Because I love Lady A and this made me feel like I was at their concert "in person."  Recommend it for sure!

Absolutely love this DVD. Had the CD first and had to get the DVD. You won't be disappointed. They give inside information themselves about what is special to them about Christmas. Really heartwarming and just think their harmonies and arrangements are the best. Merry Christmas!!
All some group love there tunes

Love this Christmas DVD.
What a great show.
Very good! Definitely one of the better Christmas concerts on dvd. I'm not a huge Lady Antebellum fan, but I collect Christmas concert dvds. This one definitely fits the holiday spirit.
